      <title>欧盟提议制裁协助俄罗斯战争的中国公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/eu-proposes-to-sanction-chinese-firms-aiding-russian-war-effort</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟提议对几家中国公司实施制裁，声称这些公司帮助俄罗斯公司开发了用于对付乌克兰的攻击无人机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/eu-proposes-to-sanction-chinese-firms-aiding-russian-war-effort</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 21:21:34 GMT</pubDate>
