    <item>
      <title>白宫要求国会额外拨款 57 亿美元弥补潜艇成本超支</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/white-house-asks-congress-for-extra-5-7-billion-for-submarine-cost-overruns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫要求国会提供约 57 亿美元的额外资金，以弥补三艘弗吉尼亚级潜艇的超支成本，以及用于船厂升级和提高工资，以吸引焊工、管道工和工程师。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/white-house-asks-congress-for-extra-5-7-billion-for-submarine-cost-overruns</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 21:02:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国经济前景恶化速度创 2022 年以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/south-koreans-economic-outlook-frays-at-fastest-pace-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国大选后，韩国央行每月进行的一项调查显示，11 月份韩国人对经济的展望以两年多来最快的速度恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/south-koreans-economic-outlook-frays-at-fastest-pace-since-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国钢铁业审查或成为共和党调查目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/us-steel-review-targeted-by-republicans-for-potential-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党议员呼吁总统乔·拜登的政府保存与美国钢铁公司拟定出售给日本新日铁公司交易有关的文件，并表示“严重担忧”，认为政治因素玷污了正在进行的对该交易的国家安全审查，并提出了国会进行调查的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/us-steel-review-targeted-by-republicans-for-potential-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 19:03:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Axios 称特朗普可能任命卡什·帕特尔出任 FBI 或司法部职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/trump-likely-to-tap-kash-patel-for-fbi-or-doj-post-axios-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Axios 援引熟悉权力交接情况的人士的话称，当选总统特朗普预计将任命卡什·帕特尔担任联邦调查局或司法部的高级职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/trump-likely-to-tap-kash-patel-for-fbi-or-doj-post-axios-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 18:59:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大食品价格上涨超过工资上涨，加剧工人焦虑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/food-inflation-in-canada-outpaces-wage-gains-fuels-worker-angst</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大的工资增长落后于食品价格的上涨，这是导致该国供应链中断的劳资冲突的主要因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/food-inflation-in-canada-outpaces-wage-gains-fuels-worker-angst</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 18:31:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>司法部将撤销华盛顿和佛罗里达对特朗普的起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/doj-formally-moves-to-drop-trump-2020-obstruction-case-in-dc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部已终止对唐纳德·特朗普的刑事指控，这标志着对这位前总统的特别联邦起诉已经结束。特朗普的连任确保了他不会在白宫受到指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/doj-formally-moves-to-drop-trump-2020-obstruction-case-in-dc</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 18:26:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚预算因结构性赤字而大幅超支</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/australia-budget-blow-out-seen-as-structural-deficit-takes-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德勤经济研究所 (Deloitte Access Economics) 表示，澳大利亚的预算赤字可能会超出预期，与前几年的情况相反，当时铁矿石价格高企带来了巨额收入提升，最终使账面转为盈余。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/australia-budget-blow-out-seen-as-structural-deficit-takes-hold</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
